			<text><![CDATA[*  This report provides a detailed overview of customer bookings, including booking dates, rental periods, and booking statuses.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="aeabc7fc-3a6f-4570-bd3b-a9ac69b12709" x="-3" y="30" width="800" height="20" fontSize="12.0" hTextAlign="Justified">
			<text><![CDATA[*  It highlights key information such as advance payments, driver assignment decisions, and special customer notes.]]></text>
